Package no.hiof.webframework.interfaces.builders

Interface IHtmlBuilder

All Known Implementing Classes:
HtmlPageBuilder
public interface IHtmlBuilder
This is an interface for building an HTML page. It defines methods for adding different sections to the page and building the final HTML page.
